; Coverage for xact.cc: fn_all - check if all postings match

2024/01/01 Transfer
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Expenses:Gas    $-10.00

2024/02/01 Mixed
    Expenses:Gas     $20.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --limit 'all(account =~ /Expenses/)'
24-Jan-01 Transfer              Expenses:Food                $10.00       $10.00
                                Expenses:Gas                $-10.00            0
end test
